---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="网球前进 Timeline">
	<main>
		<div class="py-12">
			<div class="hero container">
				<div class="hero-content text-center">
				<div class="max-w-md">
					<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">哈喽, 我是 Lantt。</h1>
					<p class="py-6">这里是我的网球改善记录以及当下的目标，如果你也喜欢网球，希望你能在这里也能有所收获。</p>
				</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<section>
			<ul class="timeline timeline-snap-icon max-md:timeline-compact timeline-vertical">
				<li>
				<div class="timeline-middle">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-start md:text-end mb-10">
					<time class="font-mono italic">2023.10</time>
					<div class="text-lg font-black">单反稳定性</div>
					减少单反掉拍头，更多的向前顶和撞，减少单反的旋转。掉拍头会来不及，先能把球回过去再说。球速更快一些，是我目前比较想要的效果。
				</div>
				<hr class="bg-primary"/>
				</li>
				<li>
				<hr class="bg-primary"/>
				<div class="timeline-middle">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-end mb-10">
					<time class="font-mono italic">2023.10</time>
					<div class="text-lg font-black">发球肩带</div>
					之前因为发球时，手臂使用力量过多，导致肩袖被拉扯受伤，现在需要更多的使用身体的力量，肩膀发力更多，减少肩膀的受伤。
				</div>
				<hr class="bg-primary"/>
				</li>
				<li>
				<hr class="bg-primary"/>
				<div class="timeline-middle">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-start md:text-end mb-10">
					<time class="font-mono italic">2024.01</time>
					<div class="text-lg font-black">平台发球向前曲膝</div>

					膝盖向前曲膝，不要重心向后，左臂尽量向后向上伸直，在身体向前时可以带动，同时可以明显感觉到身体在向前。
				</div>
				<hr class="bg-primary"/>
				</li>
				<li>
				<hr />
				<div class="timeline-middle">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-end mb-10">
					<time class="font-mono italic">2024.01</time>
					<div class="text-lg font-black">正手上旋-食指</div>
					食指最后主动发力，带动拍子。
				</div>
				<hr />
				</li>
				<li>
				<hr />
				<div class="timeline-middle">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="h-5 w-5"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-start md:text-end mb-10">
					<time class="font-mono italic">2024.01</time>
					<div class="text-lg font-black">上旋发球</div>
					身体不要完全打开
				</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
			</section>
		  <footer class="footer footer-center p-10">
			<aside>
			  <p>Copyright © 2024 - All right reserved by Lantt</p>
			</aside> 
			<nav>
			  <div class="grid grid-flow-col gap-4">
